snippet.title: Version2 Module 6 - Expanding Empathy - Interview with Daniel Schmachtenberger 1/2
snippet.description:
http://www.version2.me
This Video is a segment of the 90day beta program intended for the version2 Community. v2 was founded by software visionary Sanjiv Sidhu who built i2 Technologies and o9. Sanjiv has since been seeking a large scale solution to the worlds growing environmental crisis and has Sanjiv decided the best way to create a sustained change in how we treat the planet was by shifting human behavior. v2 is the next version of the human endeavor -- one that is empowered despite circumstance. To sign up for the next virtual event, or become part of our growing community, go to: http://www.version2.me
